{"tid":746642,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"分手後的日子","createTime":"2018-07-17T16:50:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-18T06:37:51.000Z","uid":156393,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"296a7a9e6ffeb75dbc9f3b9a5c57e498125502d8","tid":746642,"uid":156393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T16:50:57.000Z","msg":"分開了2個多月<br />\n生活沒甚麼變化 <br />\n比之前更自由 想做甚麼就去做甚麼<br />\n甚至覺得比一起的時候更快樂<br />\n分開那天至現在 <br />\n我好像沒有失戀的傷感 沒有大吵大鬧 沒有過頹廢生活<br />\n一切也很正常 <br />\n看見我們曾經的合照 我也只是偷偷的想你<br />\n朋友也說我完全不覺得我是一個剛失戀的人<br />\n我都覺得我是一個冷血的人 <br />\n<br />\n但為什麼我今天看見你whatsapp沒有icon了 <br />\n猜到你封鎖了我的時候 我會不停流淚<br />\n<br />\n分開了2個多月 我還是流淚了"},{"pid":"5be835c0233704ec8eb0309576a72f529f545d0b","tid":746642,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T17:00:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fb61caecd255d65d872bcd50c5441773a9ff841","tid":746642,"uid":31922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T17:01:23.000Z","msg":"好憎佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6381daaaf57f149317dc300e934a235bc5f706f2","tid":746642,"uid":156393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8fb61caecd255d65d872bcd50c5441773a9ff841","tid":746642,"uid":31922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T17:01:23.000Z","msg":"好憎佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T17:09:20.000Z","msg":"點解吖？"},{"pid":"2fb50889841bd7a4fc94a30ef3dd0385c64adc79","tid":746642,"uid":161352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T17:10:35.000Z","msg":"同我好似<br />\n<br />\n一直無主動愛佢 做啲咩野<br />\n拍緊同無拍無分別<br />\n有啲唔開心都只係不捨 唔係因為愛<br />\n<br />\n利申：好後悔一直唔嗲唔吊 無維繫<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17caa426d73667463312d1db0c6ef9aae55971d3","tid":746642,"uid":31922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6381daaaf57f1493